"<ulink url=\"&url_changelog;\"> &url_changelog;</ulink> ali pa sami brskate "
"po virih prek <ulink url=\"&url_git_web_kde;\">spletnega vmesnika git</"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwave; version v0.9.0 is the first version hosted on &kde; (kdereview) and "
