#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1145
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating a New File"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje nove datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can create a new and empty file menu under <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>New...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Nov in prazen meni datotek lahko ustvarite pod <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nova...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1155
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of &kwave;'s new file dialog"
msgstr "Tukaj je posnetek zaslona &kwave; pogovornega okna za novo datoteko"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1163
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the File New Dialog"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna Nova datoteka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select the sample rate, resolution in bits per sample and the number "
"of tracks. Per default the file format will be \".wav\", but it can still be "
"changed at the time when the file is saved."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko hitrost vzorčenja, ločljivost v bitih na vzorec in število "
"skladb. Privzeto bo format datoteke \".wav\", vendar ga je še vedno mogoče "
"spremeniti, ko je datoteka shranjena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The length of the new signal can be set by time (hours, minutes, seconds) or "
"by the number of samples. Additionally you can select it relative to the "
"highest possible length, which is limited by the available memory and "
"&kwave;'s internal limit (2 GB)."
msgstr ""
"Dolžino novega signala lahko nastavimo s časom (ure, minute, sekunde) ali s "
"številom vzorcev. Poleg tega ga lahko izberete glede na največjo možno "
"dolžino, ki je omejena z razpoložljivim pomnilnikom in interno omejitvijo "
"&kwave; (2 GB)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1185
#, no-c-format
msgid "Recording"
msgstr "Snemanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwave; is able to record audio data from various sources, with all sample "
"rates, sample formats and other modes that your sound hardware supports. "
"&kwave; can record with the ALSA, PulseAudio, Qt, and OSS backends."
msgstr ""
"&kwave; lahko snema zvočne podatke iz različnih virov, z vsemi stopnjami "
"vzorčenja, formati vzorčenja in drugimi načini, ki jih podpira vaša zvočna "
"strojna oprema. &kwave; lahko snema z zaledji ALSA, PulseAudio, Qt in OSS."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The recording can be reached from the menu under <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Record</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Do posnetka lahko pridete v meniju pod <menuchoice> <guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Snemaj</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here is a screenshot of the &kwave; record dialog, showing the first page "
"with the recording controls during a running recording session. Like in most "
"dialogs of &kwave; you can get some help or see tooltips on the controls."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj je posnetek zaslona &kwave; pogovornega okna za snemanje, ki prikazuje "
"prvo stran s kontrolniki za snemanje med tekočo snemalno sejo. Tako kot v "
"večini pogovornih oken &kwave; lahko dobite pomoč ali si ogledate namige "
"orodij na kontrolnikih."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1208
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of &kwave;'s record dialog"
msgstr "Tukaj je posnetek zaslona &kwave; pogovornega okna za snemanje"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1216
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Record Dialog"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna za snemanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1222
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you have the following controls:"
msgstr "Tukaj imate naslednje kontrole:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Pre-Record:</guilabel> If the pre-recording feature of &kwave; is "
"enabled and the recording is started, &kwave; records into an internal "
"buffer which is some seconds long. If you press the <guibutton>Record</"
"guibutton> ( <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"krec_record.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> "
"<phrase>record button</phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> ) button "
"again, then the recording really starts, and also keeps the already pre-"
"recorded data. This is useful for example if you want to record your "
"favorite song from radio, but you recognize too late that the song has "
"started. In this case you can still press the record button and get the "
"start of the song from what &kwave; has already pre-recorded before, so that "
"you will no longer miss a start."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pred-snemanje:</guilabel> Če je funkcija vnaprejšnjega snemanja "
"&kwave; omogočena in snemanje se začne, &kwave; zapisuje v notranji "
"medpomnilnik, ki je dolg nekaj sekund. Če pritisnete <guibutton>Snemaj</"
"guibutton> ( <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"krec_record.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> "
"<phrase>gumb za snemanje</phrase > </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> ), "
"potem se snemanje zares začne in ohrani tudi že vnaprej posnete podatke. To "
"je uporabno na primer, če želite posneti svojo najljubšo pesem z radia, "
"vendar prepozno ugotovite, da se je pesem začela. V tem primeru lahko še "
"vedno pritisnete gumb za snemanje in dobite začetek pesmi iz tega, kar je "
"&kwave; že vnaprej posnel, tako da ne boste več zamudili začetka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Record Time:</guilabel> If the length of the recording should be "
"limited to some time, you can activate this setting and select a time in "
"hours, minutes, seconds for your recording. If this option is not enabled, "
"the recording runs until you press the <guibutton>Stop</guibutton> "
"(<inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"record_stop.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject><textobject><phrase>stop button</phrase></"
"textobject> </inlinemediaobject>) button."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Čas snemanja:</guilabel> Če naj bo dolžina posnetka omejena na "
"določen čas, lahko aktivirate to nastavitev in izberete čas v urah, minutah, "
"sekundah za vaš posnetek. Če ta možnost ni omogočena, snemanje poteka, "
"dokler ne pritisnete gumba <guibutton>Ustavi</guibutton> "
"(<inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"record_stop.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject><textobject><phrase>za zaustavitev</phrase></"
"textobject> </inlinemediaobject>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Start At:</guilabel> If this setting is activated, you can set a "
"date and time when the recording will be started. Please keep in mind that "
"if the configured time is in the past, the recording will start immediately."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Začni ob:</guilabel> Če je ta nastavitev aktivirana, lahko "
"nastavite datum in uro, ko se bo snemanje začelo. Ne pozabite, da se bo "
"snemanje začelo takoj, če je nastavljeni čas v preteklosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1261
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Record Trigger:</guilabel> If enabled, the recording starts only "
"if the volume of the input goes over a certain limit, which can be defined "
"from 0 to 100% of the highest possible input volume. This is useful if you "
"do not want to record leading silence. (Hint: combine this with the "
"prerecording feature mentioned above to catch also some seconds before "
"reaching the trigger, so that you don't miss any silent fade-ins.)"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Sprožilnik snemanja:</guilabel> Če je omogočeno, se snemanje začne "
"le, če glasnost vhoda preseže določeno mejo, ki je lahko definirana od 0 do "
"100 % najvišje možne glasnosti vhoda. To je uporabno, če ne želite posneti "
"uvodne tišine. (Namig: združite to z zgoraj omenjeno funkcijo vnaprejšnjega "
"snemanja, da ujamete tudi nekaj sekund, preden dosežete sprožilnik, tako da "
"ne zamudite nobenega tihega utišanja.)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>New</guibutton> (<inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"record_new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject><textobject><phrase>new button</phrase></textobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>) button is active when the recording is not running or is "
"finished, to discard the current file content and start again."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Novo</guibutton> (<inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"record_new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject><textobject><phrase>nov gumb</phrase></textobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>) je aktiven, ko snemanje ne teče ali je končano, da "
"zavržete trenutno vsebino datoteke in začnete znova."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Stop</guibutton> (<inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"record_stop.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject><textobject><phrase>stop button</phrase></textobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>) button is active when the recording or pre-recording is "
"running or &kwave; is waiting for the trigger. If pressed, the current "
"progress will be stopped."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Ustavi</guibutton> (<inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"record_stop.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject><textobject><phrase>gumb za ustavitev</phrase></textobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>) je aktiven, ko poteka snemanje ali predsnemanje ali "
"&kwave; čaka na sprožilnik. Če pritisnete, se trenutni napredek ustavi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1287
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Pause</guibutton> (<inlinemediaobject><imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"record_pause.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject><textobject><phrase>pause button</phrase></textobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>) button is active when the recording or pre-recording is "
"running. The first time you press it, the recording will be halted and the "
"button starts blinking. When you press it again the button will stop "
"blinking and recording will continue immediately, without waiting for a "
"trigger."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Premor</guibutton> (<inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"record_pause.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject><textobject><phrase>gumb za premor</phrase></textobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>) gumb je aktiven, ko poteka snemanje ali predsnemanje. Ko "
"ga pritisnete prvič, se snemanje prekine in gumb začne utripati. Ko ga znova "
"pritisnete, bo gumb prenehal utripati in snemanje se bo nadaljevalo takoj "
"brez čakanja na sprožilnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Record</guibutton> (<inlinemediaobject><imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"krec_record.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject><textobject><phrase>record button</phrase></textobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>) button starts the recording and/or prerecording, "
"depending on the features enabled above:"
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Snemaj</guibutton> (<inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"krec_record.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject><textobject><phrase>gumb za snemanje</phrase></textobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>) začne snemanje in/ali vnaprejšnje snemanje, odvisno od "
"zgoraj omogočenih funkcij:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If neither prerecording nor trigger level are used, the recording starts as "
"soon as you press the record button."
msgstr ""
"Če ne uporabite niti predsnemanja niti ravni sprožitve, se snemanje začne "
"takoj, ko pritisnete gumb za snemanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1309
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If prerecording is not used and a trigger level is set, the first press will "
"let &kwave; wait for the trigger level to be reached. While waiting for a "
"trigger, you can force the recording to start immediately by pressing the "
"record button again, otherwise the recording will start automatically when "
"the trigger level has been reached."
msgstr ""
"Če predhodno snemanje ni uporabljeno in je nastavljena raven sprožitve, bo "
"prvi pritisk omogočil &kwave; počakajte, da je dosežena raven sprožitve. Med "
"čakanjem na sprožilnik lahko s ponovnim pritiskom na gumb za snemanje "
"prisilite, da se snemanje začne takoj, sicer se bo snemanje začelo "
"samodejno, ko je dosežena raven sprožitve."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If prerecording is enabled, the first press starts only the prerecording and "
"the second press really starts the recording."
msgstr ""
"Če je vnaprejšnje snemanje omogočeno, se s prvim pritiskom začne samo "
"predsnemanje, z drugim pritiskom pa se snemanje zares začne."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1331
#, no-c-format
msgid "Playback"
msgstr "Predvajanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1333
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Depending on the compilation options &kwave; is able to play sounds through "
"one of the following playback methods:"
msgstr ""
"Odvisno od možnosti prevajanja &kwave; lahko predvaja zvoke v enem od "
"naslednjih načinov playbacka:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1338
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"ALSA (Advanced Linux Sound Architecture): Supercedes OSS, supports more "
"features and more hardware. Might collide with other sound applications like "
"OSS does, but has a plugin called \"dmix\" as a way out. Newer versions of "
"ALSA use a dmix like plugin per default, so this should the best choice for "
"you!"
msgstr ""
"ALSA (Advanced Linux Sound Architecture): Nadomešča OSS, podpira več funkcij "
"in več strojne opreme. Lahko naleti na druge zvočne aplikacije, kot je OSS, "
"vendar ima kot izhod vtičnik, imenovan \"dmix\". Novejše različice ALSA "
"privzeto uporabljajo vtičnik, kot je dmix, zato bi to morala biti najboljša "
"izbira za vas!"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"PulseAudio: Common general purpose sound server on Linux. PulseAudio might "
"not be able to get as low latency as ALSA."
msgstr ""
"PulseAudio: skupni zvočni strežnik za splošne namene v sistemu Linux. "
"PulseAudio morda ne bo mogel doseči tako nizke zakasnitve kot ALSA."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Qt Multimedia: Not designed for low-latency audio, but works with large "
"buffer sizes."
msgstr ""
"Qt Multimedia: ni zasnovan za zvok z nizko zakasnitvijo, vendar deluje z "
"velikimi medpomnilniki."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1355
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"OSS (Open Sound System): The oldest linux implementation, capable of mono "
"and stereo output. Deprecated since linux kernel 2.6. Might collide with "
"other sound applications, only one application at a time can use OSS "
"playback !"
msgstr ""
"OSS (odprt zvočni sistem): Najstarejša izvedba Linuxa, zmožna mono in stereo "
"izhoda. Zastarel od jedra linux 2.6 naprej. Lahko naleti na druge zvočne "
"aplikacije, samo ena aplikacija naenkrat lahko uporablja playback OSS!"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Before trying to play sounds, you should take a look on the playback "
"configuration dialog:"
msgstr ""
"Preden poskušate predvajati zvoke, si oglejte pogovorno okno za "
"konfiguracijo predvajanja:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1370
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of &kwave;'s playback setup dialog"
msgstr ""
"Tukaj je posnetek zaslona &kwave; pogovornega okna za nastavitev predvajanja"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1378
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Playback Setup Dialog"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna za nastavitev predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1384
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your sound file uses more or less channels than the playback allows, all "
"channels will be mixed together during playback. For example if you have a "
"file with three channels and you use stereo playback, the left channel will "
"play channel 0 (upper) and half of channel 1 (middle), the right channel "
"will play the half of channel 1 (middle) and channel 2 (lower)."
msgstr ""
"Če vaša zvočna datoteka uporablja več ali manj kanalov, kot jih dovoljuje "
"predvajanje, bodo vsi kanali med predvajanjem pomešani. Na primer, če imate "
"datoteko s tremi kanali in uporabljate stereo predvajanje, bo levi kanal "
"predvajal kanal 0 (zgornji) in polovico kanala 1 (srednji), desni kanal pa "
"bo predvajal polovico kanala 1 (srednji) in kanal 2 (spodnji)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1392
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For getting a smooth playback without interruptions, you should also set the "
"buffer size to an appropriate value. If you encounter problems with "
"interrupted playback, you should increase the buffer size here. But the "
"bigger you set the buffer, the bigger is the latency between the audible "
"sound and the display of the playback position in the signal display."
msgstr ""
"Za nemoteno predvajanje brez prekinitev morate tudi nastaviti velikost "
"medpomnilnika na ustrezno vrednost. Če naletite na težave s prekinitvami "
"predvajanja, povečajte velikost medpomnilnika. Toda ko nastavite večji "
"medpomnilnik, je tudi večja zakasnitev med zvokom in prikazom položaja "
"predvajanja na zaslonu signala."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1400
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The playback settings dialog also provides a button for playing a simple "
"test sound. You should hear a 440Hz tone that wanders over all speakers, "
"from one to the next."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno z nastavitvami predvajanja ponuja tudi gumb za predvajanje "
"preprostega preskusnega zvoka. Slišati bi morali ton 440 Hz, ki se sprehaja "
"po vseh zvočnikih od enega do drugega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1405
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you have configured playback, you can use the playback controls of the "
"&kwave; main window or through the <menuchoice><guimenu>Play</guimenu></"
"menuchoice> menu or with keyboard shortcuts:"
msgstr ""
"Ko konfigurirate predvajanje, lahko uporabite kontrolnike za predvajanje "
"&kwave; v glavnem oknu ali prek menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Predvajaj</"
"guimenu></menuchoice> ali z bližnjicami na tipkovnici:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1411
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo><keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Play</guimenu><guimenuitem>Start</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>: Start "
"playback of the current selection from its beginning or the whole file from "
"the current cursor position if nothing was selected. Play only once."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo><keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Predvajaj</guimenu><guimenuitem>Začni</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>: "
"Začetek predvajanja trenutnega izbora od začetka ali celotna datoteka od "
"trenutnega položaja kazalca, če ni bilo nič izbrano. Predvaja se samo enkrat."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Play</guimenu><guimenuitem>Loop</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>: Like before, but repeat in a loop."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Predvajaj</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zanka</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>: Kot prej, vendar ponovitev v zanki."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1424
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo>&Space;</keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Play</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pause</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>: Pause "
"the playback at the current position. Only available when the playback is "
"running."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo>&Space;</keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Predvajaj</guimenu><guimenuitem>Premor</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>: "
"Začasno ustavi predvajanje na trenutnem mestu. Na voljo samo med "
"predvajanjem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1431
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo>&Space;</keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Play</guimenu><guimenuitem>Continue</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>: "
"Continue the playback from the position where it has been paused. Only "
"available if the playback is paused."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo>&Space;</keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Predvajaj</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nadaljuj</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>: Nadaljuje s predvajanjem od mesta, kjer je bilo zaustavljeno. "
"Na voljo samo, če je predvajanje začasno ustavljeno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1438
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo><keycap>Esc</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Play</guimenu><guimenuitem>Stop</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>: Stop "
"the playback, go back to the start of the selection."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo><keycap>Esc</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Predvajaj</guimenu><guimenuitem>Ustavi</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>: "
"ustavi predvajanje, vrne se na začetek izbire."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1452
#, no-c-format
msgid "File Properties"
msgstr "Lastnosti datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1454
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwave; is able to handle several meta information that is stored within an "
"audio file. It tries to import and export as much of that information as "
"possible. For example, if you import an MP3 file with ID3 tags, you can keep "
"that information when exporting to a Wave file. If &kwave; would lose meta "
"information when saving, it shows a warning."
msgstr ""
"&kwave; lahko obravnava več metainformacij, ki so shranjene v zvočni "
"datoteki. Poskuša uvoziti in izvoziti čim več teh informacij. Če na primer "
"uvozite datoteko MP3 z oznakami ID3, lahko te podatke obdržite pri izvozu v "
"datoteko Wave. Če bi &kwave; pri shranjevanju izgubil meta informacije, "
"prikaže opozorilo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1462
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can view and modify the meta information under <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>File Properties...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>. There you can also change things like sample format, resolution "
"and compression."
msgstr ""
"Meta informacije si lahko ogledate in jih spremenite pod <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Lastnosti datoteke...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>. Tam lahko spremenite tudi stvari, kot so format vzorca, "
"ločljivost in stiskanje."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1471
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of &kwave;'s file properties dialog"
msgstr ""
"Tukaj je posnetek zaslona &kwave; pogovornega okna z lastnostmi datoteke"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1479
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the File Properties Dialog"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna z lastnostmi datoteke"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1490
#, no-c-format
msgid "Zooming and navigating"
msgstr "Povečevanje in navigacija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1492
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwave; provides several ways to zoom and navigate, using keyboard "
"shortcuts, menu commands, toolbar buttons and by using the mouse. The "
"following sections should give an overview on how to use all of these "
"functions."
msgstr ""
"&kwave; ponuja več načinov povečave in krmarjenja z uporabo bližnjic na "
"tipkovnici, menijskih ukazov, gumbov v orodni vrstici in z uporabo miške. "
"Naslednji razdelki naj bi podali pregled uporabe vseh teh funkcij."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1499
#, no-c-format
msgid "Zooming in and out"
msgstr "Povečevanje in pomanjševanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>zoom in:</emphasis> zooms in to see more details, magnifies by "
"factor 3."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>povečaj:</emphasis> poveča za ogled več podrobnosti, poveča za "
"faktor 3."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1507
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"menu entry / keyboard shortcut: <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>+</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>View</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Zoom In</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"menijski vnos / bližnjica na tipkovnici: <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>+</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Povečaj</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1517
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>zoom out:</emphasis> zooms in to see less details, shrinks by "
"factor 3."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>pomanjšaj:</emphasis> poveča, da vidi manj podrobnosti, skrči za "
"faktor 3."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1521
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"menu entry / keyboard shortcut: <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>-</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>View</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Zoom Out</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"menijski vnos / bližnjica na tipkovnici: <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>-</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pomanjšaj</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1531
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>zoom selection:</emphasis> zooms to a factor where the current "
"selection is completely visible in the current view."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>pomanjšava izbire:</emphasis> poveča na faktor, kjer je trenutna "
"izbira popolnoma vidna v trenutnem pogledu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1536
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"menu entry / keyboard shortcut: <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"&Space;</keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zoom to "
"Selection</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"menijski vnos / bližnjica na tipkovnici: <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;&Space;</keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Povečaj na izbor</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1546
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>zoom to whole signal:</emphasis> selects a zoom factor that makes "
"the whole signal visible in the current window."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>povečaj na celoten signal:</emphasis> izbere faktor povečave, "
"zaradi katerega je celoten signal viden v trenutnem oknu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1551
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"menu entry: <menuchoice> <guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zoom to whole "
"signal</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"menijski vnos: <menuchoice> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Povečava "
"na celoten signal</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1560
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>zoom to 100%:</emphasis> zooms in up to a scale where one sample "
"is represented by one pixel on the screen."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>povečaj na 100 %:</emphasis> poveča do lestvice, kjer en vzorec "
"predstavlja ena slikovna pika na zaslonu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1565
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"menu entry: <menuchoice> <guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zoom to 100%</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"menijski vnos: <menuchoice> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Povečava "
"do 100 %</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1574
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>select predefined zoom:</emphasis> select a zoom factor from the "
"zoom combo box in the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>izberite vnaprej določeno povečavo:</emphasis> izberite faktor "
"povečave v kombiniranem polju za povečavo v orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1583
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrolling left and right"
msgstr "Drsenje levo in desno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1587
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>goto position:</emphasis> opens a dialog to enter the position "
"where you want scrolls the current view."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>pojdi na položaj:</emphasis> odpre pogovorno okno za vnos "
"položaja, kjer želite, da se pomika trenutni pogled."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1591
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"menu entry / keyboard shortcut: <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>G</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>View</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Go to Position...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"menijski vnos / bližnjica na tipkovnici: <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>G</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pojdi na položaj... </guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1600
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>to begin:</emphasis> scrolls the current view so that it starts at "
"the beginning of the signal."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>za začetek:</emphasis> premika trenutni pogled tako, da se začne "
"na začetku signala."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1605
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"menu entry / keyboard shortcut: <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;&Home;"
"</keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Begin</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"menijski vnos / bližnjica na tipkovnici: <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;&Home;</keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Začetek</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1614
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>to end:</emphasis> scrolls the current view so that it ends at the "
"end of the signal."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>do konca:</emphasis> premika trenutni pogled tako, da se konča na "
"koncu signala."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1618
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"menu entry / keyboard shortcut: <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;&End;"
"</keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>End</guimenuitem> "
"</menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"menijski vnos / bližnjica na tipkovnici: <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;&End;</keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konec</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1627
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>previous page:</emphasis> scrolls to the position right before the "
"current view (left)."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>prejšnja stran:</emphasis> se pomakne na položaj tik pred "
"trenutnim pogledom (levo)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1631
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"menu entry / keyboard shortcut: <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo>&PgUp;</"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Previous Page</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"menijski vnos / bližnjica na tipkovnici: <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut><keycombo>&PgUp;</keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Prejšnja stran</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1640
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>next page:</emphasis> scrolls to the position right after the "
"current view (right)."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>naslednja stran:</emphasis> se pomakne na položaj takoj za "
"trenutnim pogledom (desno)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1644
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"menu entry / keyboard shortcut: <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo>&PgDn;</"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Next Page</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"menijski vnos / bližnjica na tipkovnici: <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut><keycombo>&PgDn;</keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Naslednja stran</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1653
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>scroll right:</emphasis> scrolls to the end of the signal by 1/3 "
"of the current view."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>pomik desno:</emphasis> pomikanje do konca signala za 1/3 "
"trenutnega pogleda."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1657
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"menu entry / keyboard shortcut: <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo>&Right;</"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Scroll right</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"menijski vnos / bližnjica na tipkovnici: <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut><keycombo>&Right;</keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Pomakni se desno</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1666
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>scroll left:</emphasis> scrolls to the start of the signal by 1/3 "
"of the current view."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>pomik levo:</emphasis> pomikanje na začetek signala za 1/3 "
"trenutnega pogleda."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1670
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"menu entry / keyboard shortcut: <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo>&Left;</"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Scroll left</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"menijski vnos / bližnjica na tipkovnici: <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut><keycombo>&Left;</keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Pomik levo</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1682
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the overview"
msgstr "Uporaba pregleda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1684
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main screen of &kwave; shows a small <emphasis>overview</emphasis> of "
"the whole signal above the horizontal scroll bar of the main window. This "
"overview also provides some functionality for navigating:"
msgstr ""
"Glavni zaslon &kwave; prikazuje majhen <emphasis>pregled</emphasis> "
"celotnega signala nad vodoravnim drsnim trakom glavnega okna. Ta pregled "
"ponuja tudi nekaj funkcij za krmarjenje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1690
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>single click with &LMB;</emphasis>: directly move the current view "
"to the clicked position."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>enojni klik z &LMB;</emphasis>: neposredno premakne trenutni "
"pogled na položaj klika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1695
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>double click with &LMB;</emphasis>: directly move the current view "
"to the clicked position and additionally zoom in."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>dvoklik z &LMB;</emphasis>: neposredno premakne trenutni pogled na "
"kliknjeno mesto in ga dodatno poveča."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1701
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>double click with &LMB;, with &Shift; pressed</emphasis>: directly "
"move the current view to the clicked position and additionally zoom out."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>dvokliknite z &LMB;, s &Shift; pritisnjeno</emphasis>: neposredno "
"premakne trenutni pogled na kliknjeni položaj in dodatno pomanjša."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1712
#, no-c-format
msgid "Vertical zoom"
msgstr "Navpični zoom"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1713
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can zoom the current view vertically by pressing the &Alt; key and "
"scrolling with the mouse wheel."
msgstr ""
"Trenutni pogled lahko navpično povečate tako, da pritisnete &Alt; tipko in "
"premikanje s kolescem miške."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1724
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to select"
msgstr "Kako izbrati"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1726
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwave; allows you to select a continuous range of samples as well as any "
"combination of channels (if you edit a multi-channel file). By selecting a "
"range of samples (time scope) all following commands will be limited to that "
"range and by de-selecting a channel its content will not be changed."
msgstr ""
"&kwave; omogoča izbiro neprekinjenega obsega vzorcev kot tudi poljubne "
"kombinacije kanalov (če urejate večkanalno datoteko). Z izbiro obsega "
"vzorcev (časovni obseg) bodo vsi naslednji ukazi omejeni na ta obseg in s "
"preklicem izbire kanala njegova vsebina ne bo spremenjena."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1733
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting channels"
msgstr "Izbira kanalov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1734
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting or de-selecting a channel is quite simple. Just click on the lamp "
"symbol on the left side of the signal to toggle its state:"
msgstr ""
"Izbira ali preklic izbire kanala je precej preprosta. Samo kliknite na "
"simbol lučke na levi strani signala, da preklopite njegovo stanje:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1743
#, no-c-format
msgid "green lamp"
msgstr "zelena svetilka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1744
#, no-c-format
msgid "a green lamp means \"enabled\", whereas"
msgstr "zelena lučka pomeni \"omogočeno\", medtem ko"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1752
#, no-c-format
msgid "red lamp"
msgstr "rdeča lučka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1753
#, no-c-format
msgid "a red lamp means \"disabled\"."
msgstr "rdeča lučka pomeni \"onemogočen\"."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1757
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note: If a channel is de-selected it will also not be audible for playback!"
msgstr "Opomba: Če kanal ni izbran, tudi ne bo slišen za predvajanje!"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1762
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting samples"
msgstr "Izbira vzorcev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1764
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select a range of samples in &kwave;, that range will be "
"<emphasis>inclusive</emphasis>. That means that the first and the last "
"selected sample both belong to the selection and will be used for the "
"following actions. So even if you not selected a <emphasis>range</emphasis> "
"but only a single sample, the selection will never be really \"empty\". So "
"for example if you see no selected range, the \"delete\" function applies to "
"that single sample."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete obseg vzorcev v &kwave;, bo ta obseg <emphasis>vključujoč</"
"emphasis>. To pomeni, da prvi in zadnji izbrani vzorec pripadata izboru in "
"bosta uporabljena za naslednja dejanja. Tudi če niste izbrali "
"<emphasis>razpona</emphasis>, ampak samo en vzorec, izbor nikoli ne bo zares "
"\"prazen\". Torej, če na primer ne vidite nobenega izbranega obsega, se "
"funkcija »izbriši« uporablja za ta posamezen vzorec."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1774
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The easiest way of selecting a range of samples is just to do that with "
"mouse. It works like you are used from other applications: just press the "
"&LMB; at the point you want to let the selection start and release the "
"button where you want it to end."
msgstr ""
"Najlažji način za izbiro niza vzorcev je, da to storite z miško. Deluje, kot "
"ste vajeni iz drugih aplikacij: samo pritisnite &LMB; na točki, kjer želite, "
"da se izbira začne, in spustite gumb, kjer želite, da se konča."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1780
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to adjust or move the selection's start or end, you can move the "
"mouse cursor near to the start or the end of the selection until it changes "
"from the standard arrow cursor into the left-right arrow cursor and then "
"press the &LMB; and adjust."
msgstr ""
"Če želite prilagoditi ali premakniti začetek ali konec izbora, lahko "
"premaknete kazalec miške blizu začetka ali konca izbora, dokler se ne "
"spremeni iz standardnega puščičnega kazalca v puščični kazalec levo-desno in "
"nato pritisnete &LMB; in prilagodite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1786
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also extend or shrink the selection to a specific point by holding "
"down the &Shift; key while clicking with the &LMB;. Depending on which "
"border is nearer, the left or right border of the selection will be set "
"until the new position. If there was nothing selected, will be set from the "
"beginning."
msgstr ""
"Izbor lahko tudi razširite ali skrčite na določeno točko tako, da držite "
"&Shift; med klikanjem z &LMB;. Odvisno od tega, katera meja je bližja, bo "
"leva ali desna meja izbora nastavljena do novega položaja. Če ni bilo nič "
"izbrano, bo nastavljeno od začetka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1793
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are also some functions available via the menu and of course some "
"keyboard shortcuts:"
msgstr ""
"Na voljo so tudi nekatere funkcije prek menija in seveda nekaj bližnjic na "
"tipkovnici:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1797
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"select the whole signal: <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>A</"
"keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Selection</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>All</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"izberite celoten signal: <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>A</"
"keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izbor</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem >Vse</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1804
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"select a range: <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo><keycap>R</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Selection</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Range</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"izberite obseg: <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo><keycap>R</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izbor</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Obseg</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1811
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"the currently visible area: <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo><keycap>V</"
"keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Selection</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Visible Area</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"trenutno vidno območje: <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo><keycap>V</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izbor</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Vidno Območje</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1818
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"the next block of samples, starting one sample after the end of the current "
"selection and with the same length: <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo>&Shift;"
"<keycap>+</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Selection</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Next</guimenuitem> "
"</menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"naslednji blok vzorcev, z začetkom enega vzorca po koncu trenutne izbire in "
"z enako dolžino: <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo>&Shift;<keycap>+</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izbor</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Naprej</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1826
#, no-c-format
msgid "(Hint: use the \"<keycap>+</keycap>\" key from the numeric keypad!)"
msgstr ""
"(Namig: uporabite tipko \"<keycap>+</keycap>\" na številski tipkovnici!)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1829
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"the previous block of samples, ending one sample before the start of the "
"current selection and with the same length: <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut><keycombo>&Shift;<keycap>-</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Selection</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Previous</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"prejšnji blok vzorcev, ki se konča en vzorec pred začetkom trenutnega izbora "
"in z enako dolžino: <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo>&Shift;<keycap>-</"
"keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izbor</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Prejšnji</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1837
#, no-c-format
msgid "(Hint: use the \"<keycap>-</keycap>\" key from the numeric keypad!)"
msgstr ""
"(Namig: uporabite tipko \"<keycap>-</keycap>\" na številski tipkovnici!)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1840
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"remove any selection and select \"nothing\": <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut><keycombo><keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Selection</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Nothing</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"odstranite morebitno izbiro in izberite \"nič\": <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut><keycombo><keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Izbor</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Nič</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1847
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"expand the selection to the start of the signal (first sample): <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut><keycombo>&Shift;&Home;</keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Selection</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>To Start</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"razširi izbor na začetek signala (prvi vzorec): <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut><keycombo>&Shift;&Home;</keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Izbor</guimenuitem ><guimenuitem>Za začetek</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1854
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"expand the selection to the end of the signal (last sample): <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut><keycombo>&Shift;&End;</keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Selection</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>To End</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"razširi izbor do konca signala (zadnji vzorec): <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut><keycombo>&Shift;&End;</keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Izbor</guimenuitem ><guimenuitem>Na konec</guimenuitem> "
"</menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1862
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"expand the current selection left and right up to the next label (or start/"
"end of the signal if there is none), starting at the current cursor "
"position: <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo><keycap>E</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Selection</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Expand to labels</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"razširi trenutni izbor levo in desno navzgor do naslednje oznake (ali "
"začetka/konca signala, če tega ni), začenši na trenutnem položaju kazalca: "
"<menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo><keycap>E</keycap> </keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izbor</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Razširi "
"na oznake</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1872
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"select the area between the next two labels that are right from the current "
"selection or up to the end of the signal: <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Selection</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>To "
"Next Labels</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"izberi območje med naslednjima dvema oznakama, ki sta desno od trenutnega "
"izbora ali do konca signala: <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;"
"<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Izbor</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Na naslednje oznake</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1880
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"select the area between the previous two labels that are left from the "
"current selection or up to the start of the signal: <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Selection</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>To "
"Previous Labels</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"izberi območje med prejšnjima dvema oznakama, ki sta levo od trenutne izbire "
"ali do začetka signala: <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;"
"<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Izbor</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Na prejšnje oznake</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1898
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clipboard"
msgstr "Odložišče"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1900
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwave; uses the clipboard of &plasma;. This way it is possible to exchange "
"audio data between different &kwave; windows. It might be possible as well "
"to exchange data between &kwave; and other audio applications, depending on "
"their ability to use the &plasma; clipboard."
msgstr ""
"&kwave; uporablja odložišče &plasma;. Na ta način je mogoče izmenjevati "
"zvočne podatke med različnimi okni &kwave;. Mogoča je tudi izmenjava "
"podatkov med &kwave; in drugimi zvočnimi aplikacijami, odvisno od njihove "
"zmožnosti uporabe &plasma; odložišča."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1908
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When copying data to the clipboard through the <literal>copy</literal> "
"function &kwave; uses the mime type <literal>audio/vnd.wave</literal> as "
"data format, conforming to <ulink url=\"&url_rfc2361;\">RFC 2361</ulink> "
"which is the same as the well known <literal>wav</literal> format. When "
"pasting from the clipboard into &kwave; all data formats that are available "
"as file import formats are supported, like for example Ogg/Vorbis, FLAC and "
"so on."
msgstr ""
"Pri kopiranju podatkov v odložišče prek funkcije <literal>kopiraj</literal> "
"&kwave; uporablja vrsto mime <literal>audio/vnd.wave</literal> kot format "
"podatkov, ki ustreza <ulink url=\"&url_rfc2361;\">RFC 2361</ulink>, ki je "
"enak dobro znani obliki <literal>wav</literal>. Pri lepljenju iz odložišča v "
"&kwave; so podprti vsi formati podatkov, ki so na voljo kot formati za uvoz "
"datotek, kot na primer Ogg/Vorbis, FLAC itd."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1925
#, no-c-format
msgid "Drag and Drop"
msgstr "Povleci in spusti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1927
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwave; supports the &kde-frameworks; Drag and Drop protocol. This enables "
"you to open files just by picking them up in a &dolphin; or &konqueror; "
"window or the Desktop and let them drop into a window of &kwave;."
msgstr ""
"&kwave; podpira &kde-frameworks; protokol povleci in spusti. To vam omogoča "
"odpiranje datotek tako, da jih poberete v &dolphin; ali &konqueror; okno ali "
"namizje in pustite, da se spustijo v okno &kwave;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1933
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please note that if you drop a file into a &kwave; window that already "
"contains an opened file, the currently opened file will be closed first and "
"then the file you dropped will be opened in it. If you don't want that, you "
"should open a new empty &kwave; window first."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da če spustite datoteko v &kwave; okno, ki že vsebuje odprto "
"datoteko, bo trenutno odprta datoteka najprej zaprta, nato pa se bo v njej "
"odprla datoteka, ki ste jo spustili. Če tega ne želite, raje odprite novo "
"prazno okno &kwave;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1940
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also select a range of samples and drag or drop them into a &kwave; "
"window. Per default the drag operation is done in <emphasis>move</emphasis> "
"mode where the selected range is deleted from the original place and "
"inserted at the drop position. By pressing the &Ctrl; key you can modify "
"this and drag in <emphasis>copy</emphasis> mode instead."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko tudi vrsto vzorcev in jih povlečete ali spustite v okno "
"&kwave;. Privzeto se operacija vlečenja izvede v načinu <emphasis>premakni</"
"emphasis>, kjer se izbrani obseg izbriše s prvotnega mesta in vstavi na "
"mesto za spuščanje. S pritiskom na &Ctrl; lahko to spremenite in namesto "
"tega povlečete v načinu <emphasis>kopiraj</emphasis>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2037
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automization and Scripting with &kwave;"
msgstr "Avtomatizacija in skriptiranje z &kwave;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2038
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwave; since its first version uses an internal text command language. This "
"command language is used internally for menu handling, &GUI; control, "
"builtin effects and plugin invocations. The commands will be described later "
"in the section <link linkend=\"kwave_commands\" endterm="
"\"title_kwave_commands\"></link>."
msgstr ""
"&kwave; od prve različice uporablja interni besedilni ukazni jezik. Ta "
"ukazni jezik se interno uporablja za upravljanje menijev, &GUI; nadzor, "
"vgrajeni učinki in priklici vtičnikov. Ukazi bodo opisani pozneje v razdelku "
"<link linkend=\"kwave_commands\" endterm=\"title_kwave_commands\"></link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2046
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Syntax"
msgstr "Splošna sintaksa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2049
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All commands consist of a <emphasis>command name</emphasis> and an optional "
"<emphasis>parameter list</emphasis> in round brackets, depending on the "
"command."
msgstr ""
"Vsi ukazi so sestavljeni iz <emphasis>imena ukaza</emphasis> in neobveznega "
"<emphasis>seznama parametrov</emphasis> v okroglih oklepajih, odvisno od "
"ukaza."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2054
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allowed characters for command names are <emphasis>letters</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>digits</emphasis> and <emphasis>colon</emphasis>. Commands are "
"case sensitive and are always in lower case."
msgstr ""
"Dovoljeni znaki za imena ukazov so <emphasis>črke</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>števke</emphasis> in <emphasis>dvopičje</emphasis>. Ukazi so "
"občutljivi na velike in male črke in so vedno napisani z malimi črkami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2059
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Parameters within a parameter list are separated by <emphasis>comma</"
"emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Parametri na seznamu parametrov so ločeni z <emphasis>vejico</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2063
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Numerical parameters can be given as fixed point numbers or as floating "
"point numbers, <emphasis>using a dot as decimal separator</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Številske parametre lahko podate kot števila s fiksno vejico ali kot števila "
"s plavajočo vejico, pri čemer <emphasis>uporabite piko kot decimalno ločilo</"
"emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2067
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String parameters are automatically trimmed (all white space at the start "
"and at the end is removed). If that is not wanted, they can be surrounded by "
"double quotes (<token>&quot;</token>). If a string parameter contains "
"special characters (like <quote><token>,</token></quote>, <quote><token>;</"
"token></quote>, <quote><token>#</token></quote> or a <quote><token>&bsol;</"
"token></quote> itself), these special characters have to be escaped by "
"preceding a <quote><token>&bsol;</token></quote>."
msgstr ""
"Parametri niza so samodejno obrezani (odstranjen je ves prazen prostor na "
"začetku in na koncu). Če tega ne želite, jih lahko obdate z dvojnimi "
"narekovaji (<token>&quot;</token>). Če parameter niza vsebuje posebne znake "
"(kot so <quote><token>,</token></quote>, <quote><token>;</token></quote>, "
"<quote><token>#</token></quote> ali sam <quote><token>&bsol;</token></"
"quote>), je treba te posebne znake ubežati tako, da pred <quote><token>&bsol;"
"</token></quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2079
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Multiple commands can be concatenated to a <emphasis>command list</emphasis> "
"by using a <quote>;</quote> as separator."
msgstr ""
"Več ukazov je mogoče združiti v <emphasis>seznam ukazov</emphasis> z uporabo "
"<quote>;</quote> kot ločila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2083
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Example: <screen><command>fileinfo(<parameter>Comments</parameter><token>,</"
"token><parameter>\"This is an \\\"example\\\" comment.\"</parameter>)</"
"command></screen> This example consists of the command <command>fileinfo</"
"command>() and has two parameters: the keyword <parameter>Comments</"
"parameter> and the text <quote><parameter>\"This is an \\\"example\\\" "
"comment.\"</parameter></quote>. (These parameters are explained in the "
"corresponding section in the command reference)."
msgstr ""
"Primer: <screen><command>fileinfo(<parameter>Komentarji</parameter><token>,</"
"token><parameter>\"To je komentar \\\"primer\\.\"</parameter>)</command></"
"screen> Ta primer je sestavljen iz ukaza <command>fileinfo</command>() in "
"ima dva parametra: ključno besedo <parameter>Comments</parameter> in "
"besedilo <quote><parameter>»This is an \\\"primer\\\" komentar.\"</"
"parameter></quote>. (Ti parametri so razloženi v ustreznem razdelku v sklicu "
"na ukaz)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2097
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Command Line"
msgstr "Uporaba ukazne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2098
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition to the command line options listed in the section <link linkend="
"\"command_line\">Command Line</link> which are used to start &kwave; in "
"iconified mode or without splash screen, you can pass text commands on the "
"command line, encoded in a special &URI; format:"
msgstr ""
"Poleg možnosti ukazne vrstice, navedenih v razdelku <link linkend="
"\"command_line\">Ukazna vrstica</link>, ki se uporabljajo za zagon &kwave; v "
"ikoniziranem načinu ali brez pozdravnega zaslona lahko posredujete besedilne "
"ukaze v ukazni vrstici, kodirane v posebnem &URI; format:"

#. Tag: literal
#: index.docbook:2106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"kwave:<replaceable>command</replaceable>[?<replaceable>parameter</"
"replaceable>[,<replaceable>parameter</replaceable> ...] ]"
msgstr ""
"kwave:<replaceable>ukaz</replaceable>[?<replaceable>parameter</replaceable>[,"
"<replaceable>parameter</replaceable> ...] ]"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The rules for transforming a &kwave; text command into a valid &URI; are as "
"follows:"
msgstr ""
"Pravila za preoblikovanje &kwave; besedilnega ukaza v veljaven &URI; so "
"naslednji:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &URI; starts with the word <literal>kwave</literal>, followed by a "
"<quote><token>:</token></quote> and the command name."
msgstr ""
"&URI; se začne z besedo <literal>kwave</literal>, ki ji sledi <quote><token>:"
"</token></quote> in ime ukaza."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the command has parameters, they have to be appended after the command "
"name, using a <quote><token>?</token></quote> as separator."
msgstr ""
"Če ima ukaz parametre, jih je treba pripeti za imenom ukaza z uporabo "
"<quote><token>?</token></quote> kot ločilom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Multiple parameters can be appended by using a <quote><token>,</token></"
"quote> as separator."
msgstr ""
"Več parametrov je mogoče dodati z uporabo <quote><token>,</token></quote> "
"kot ločilom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All special characters in command name and parameters have to be &URL; "
"encoded. Here a list of the translations:"
msgstr ""
"Vsi posebni znaki v imenu in parametrih ukaza morajo biti &URL; kodirani. "
"Tukaj je seznam prevodov:"

