#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2210
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kwave; Script Files"
msgstr "&kwave; Skriptne datoteke"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2211
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Structure"
msgstr "Splošna struktura"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A &kwave; <emphasis>script</emphasis> consists of a list of lines, where "
"each line can be:"
msgstr ""
"A &kwave; <emphasis>skript</emphasis> je sestavljen iz seznama vrstic, kjer "
"je vsaka vrstica lahko:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2217
#, no-c-format
msgid "a single <emphasis>command</emphasis>,"
msgstr "en sam <emphasis>ukaz</emphasis>,"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"a <emphasis>command list</emphasis>, with two or more commands concatenated "
"by a <quote><token>;</token></quote>."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>seznam ukazov</emphasis> z dvema ali več ukazi, povezanimi z "
"<quote><token>;</token></quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2226
#, no-c-format
msgid "a <emphasis>comment</emphasis>,"
msgstr "<emphasis>komentar</emphasis>,"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2229
#, no-c-format
msgid "a <emphasis>label</emphasis>"
msgstr "<emphasis>oznaka</emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2232
#, no-c-format
msgid "or an <emphasis>empty line</emphasis>, that contains white space only"
msgstr ""
"ali <emphasis>prazna vrstica</emphasis>, ki vsebuje samo prazen prostor"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2238
#, no-c-format
msgid "Comments and Empty Lines"
msgstr "Komentarji in prazne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All characters that follow a <quote><token>#</token></quote> (except when "
"used in quotes or when escaped) are treated as comments, they will be "
"silently ignored."
msgstr ""
"Vsi znaki, ki sledijo <quote><token>#</token></quote> (razen če so "
"uporabljeni v narekovajih ali ko so ubežni), se obravnavajo kot komentarji "
"in bodo tiho prezrti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2244
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lines that contain only white space or comments are ignored as well."
msgstr ""
"Vrstice, ki vsebujejo le prazen prostor ali komentarje, so prav tako prezrte."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2249
#, no-c-format
msgid "Termination"
msgstr "Prekinitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2250
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A &kwave; script terminates either when all commands have been executed "
"successfully without an error or when a command has returned an error code. "
"There is no special command for aborting the execution of a script. If you "
"want to implement a possibility for the user to end a script, you can use "
"the command <quote><link linkend=\"cmd_sect_msgbox\"><command>msgbox</"
"command></link>(<parameter><replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>)</"
"quote>. This shows a message box with the two buttons <guibutton>OK</"
"guibutton> (which lets the script continue) and <guibutton>Cancel</"
"guibutton> (which returns an error code and stops the script)."
msgstr ""
"&kwave; skript se zaključi, ko so bili vsi ukazi uspešno izvedeni brez "
"napake ali ko je ukaz vrnil kodo napake. Posebnega ukaza za prekinitev "
"izvajanja skripta ni. Če želite implementirati možnost, da uporabnik "
"zaključi skript, lahko uporabite ukaz <quote><link linkend=\"cmd_sect_msgbox"
"\"><command>msgbox</command></link>(<parameter><replaceable> besedilo</"
"replaceable></parameter>)</quote>. To prikaže okno s sporočilom z dvema "
"gumboma <guibutton>V redu</guibutton> (ki omogoča nadaljevanje skripta) in "
"<guibutton>Prekliči</guibutton> (ki vrne kodo napake in ustavi skript)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2263
#, no-c-format
msgid "Labels"
msgstr "Oznake"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lines that consist only of an identifier, followed by a <quote><token>:</"
"token></quote> are treated <emphasis>labels</emphasis>. They can be "
"referenced later in the script by the special keyword <command>GOTO</"
"command> <footnote><para>Note: Please don't mix up the keyword "
"<quote><command>GOTO</command></quote> with the text command <quote><link "
"linkend=\"cmd_sect_goto\"><command>goto</command></link> "
"(<parameter><replaceable>position</replaceable></parameter>)</quote> ! </"
"para></footnote> , which makes the execution of the script continue at the "
"location of that label (see example below)."
msgstr ""
"Vrstice, ki so sestavljene samo iz identifikatorja, ki mu sledi "
"<quote><token>:</token></quote>, se obravnavajo kot <emphasis>oznake</"
"emphasis>. Nanje se lahko pozneje v skriptu sklicujete s posebno ključno "
"besedo <command>GOTO</command> <footnote><para>Opomba: Ne zamenjujte ključne "
"besede <quote><command>GOTO</command></quote > z besedilnim ukazom "
"<quote><link linkend=\"cmd_sect_goto\"><command>goto</command></link> "
"(<parameter><replaceable>position</replaceable></parameter>)</quote> ! </"
"para></footnote> , zaradi česar se izvajanje skripta nadaljuje na lokaciji "
"te oznake (glejte primer spodaj)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A line that contains a label must not contain any other content (except "
"comments or white space) after the <quote><token>:</token></quote>."
msgstr ""
"Vrstica, ki vsebuje oznako, ne sme vsebovati nobene druge vsebine (razen "
"komentarjev ali presledka) za <quote><token>:</token></quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2281
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "Primer:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:2283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<replaceable>start:</replaceable><literal>  # &lt;= this is a label</"
"literal>\n"
"            <literal>        # do something...</literal>\n"
"            <literal>        </literal><command>msgbox</"
"command>(<parameter>once again?</parameter>)\n"
"            <literal>        </literal><command>GOTO <parameter>start</"
"parameter></command>"
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>start:</replaceable><literal>  # &lt;= to je oznaka</literal>\n"
"            <literal>        # naredi nekaj...</literal>\n"
"            <literal>        </literal><command>msgbox</"
"command>(<parameter>še enkrat?</parameter>)\n"
"            <literal>        </literal><command>GOTO <parameter>start</"
"parameter></command>"

