#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4562
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_band_pass; (Band Pass Filter)"
msgstr "&no-i18n-plugin_band_pass; (Band Pass Filter - pasovni filter)"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:4570
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Band Pass Filter Plugin"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona vtičnika Band Pass Filter"

#. Tag: literal
#: index.docbook:4577
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_band_pass;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-plugin_band_pass;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4586
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Applies a simple band pass filter to the current selection. A band pass lets "
"a certain range of frequencies around a <emphasis>center frequency</"
"emphasis> pass and filters out frequencies that are below or above the "
"center frequency by more than half of the <emphasis>bandwidth</emphasis> of "
"the filter."
msgstr ""
"Uporabi preprost pasovni filter za trenutno izbiro. Pasovni prehod omogoča "
"prehod določenemu obsegu frekvenc okoli <emphasis>centralne frekvence</"
"emphasis> in filtrira frekvence, ki so pod ali nad središčno frekvenco za "
"več kot polovico <emphasis>pasovne širine</emphasis> filtra ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4592
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The filter has grade two and is implemented as described in the book "
"<citetitle>\"An introduction to digital filter theory\"</citetitle> by "
"<author> <personname> <firstname>Julius O.</firstname> <surname>Smith</"
"surname> </personname> </author> and in Moore's book, where the normalized "
"version from Moore's book is used."
msgstr ""
"Filter ima drugo stopnjo in je implementiran, kot je opisano v knjigi "
"<citetitle>\"An introduction to digital filter theory - Uvod v teorijo "
"digitalnih filtrov\"</citetitle> avtorja <author> <personname> "
"<firstname>Julius O.</firstname> <surname>Smith</surname> </personname> </"
"author> in v Moorovi knjigi, kjer je uporabljena normalizirana različica iz "
"Moorove knjige."

