#: index.docbook:6900
#, no-c-format
msgid "Triangular window"
msgstr "Trikotno okno"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6910
#, no-c-format
msgid "use colors"
msgstr "uporabi barve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6912
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If set to non-zero, use colors for intensity, if set to zero use grayscales."
msgstr ""
"Če je nastavljeno na nič, uporabi barve za intenzivnost, če je nastavljeno "
"na nič, uporabi sive odtenke."

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:6920
#, no-c-format
msgid "track changes"
msgstr "sledi spremembam"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6922
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If set to non-zero, the sonagram will be updated when the area that was "
"evaluated has changed. If set to zero it will never be updated."
msgstr ""
"Če je nastavljeno na nič, bo sonagram posodobljen, ko se spremeni območje, "
"ki je bilo ocenjeno. Če je nastavljen na nič, ne bo nikoli posodobljen."

#. Tag: replaceable
