#, no-c-format
msgid "follow selection"
msgstr "sledi izboru"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6933
#, no-c-format
msgid "Not yet implemented, use zero for this parameter."
msgstr "Še ni implementirano, za ta parameter uporabite nič."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:6946
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_stringenter; (Enter Command)"
msgstr "&no-i18n-plugin_stringenter;  (Enter Command - Vnesite ukaz)"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:6954
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Enter Command Plugin"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona vtičnika Enter Command"

#. Tag: literal
#: index.docbook:6961
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_stringenter;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-plugin_stringenter;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6970
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A small dialog window that allows to enter a &kwave; text command. Please "
"refer to the chapter <link linkend=\"kwave_commands\" endterm="
"\"title_kwave_commands\"></link> in this manual."
msgstr ""
"Majhno pogovorno okno, ki omogoča vnos &kwave; besedilni ukaz. Glejte "
"poglavje <link linkend=\"kwave_commands\" endterm=\"title_kwave_commands\"></"
"link> v tem priročniku."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:6983
#, no-c-format
msgid "<replaceable>preset</replaceable> (optional)"
msgstr "<replaceable>prednastavitev</replaceable> (neobvezno)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:6985
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A text that is shown in the edit field when entering the dialog. This "
"parameter is optional, if omitted the edit field of the dialog will be empty "
"at start."
msgstr ""
"Besedilo, ki je prikazano v polju za urejanje ob vstopu v pogovorno okno. Ta "
"parameter ni obvezen; če ga izpustite, bo polje za urejanje pogovornega okna "
"na začetku prazno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:7000
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_volume; (Volume)"
msgstr "&no-i18n-plugin_volume; (Volume  - Glasnost)"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:7008
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Volume Plugin"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona vtičnika Volume"

#. Tag: literal
#: index.docbook:7015
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_volume;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-plugin_volume;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7024
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With this plugin you can change the volume of the current selection by a "
"constant factor. The corresponding dialog allows to enter this factor as a "
"<emphasis>numeric factor</emphasis> given as a floating point value between "
"0.10 and 10.0, a <emphasis>percentage</emphasis> between 1 and 1000, or in "
"<emphasis>decibel</emphasis> between -21 and +21."
msgstr ""
"S tem vtičnikom lahko spremenite glasnost trenutne izbire s stalnim "
"faktorjem. Ustrezno pogovorno okno omogoča vnos tega faktorja kot "
"<emphasis>številskega faktorja</emphasis>, podanega kot vrednost s plavajočo "
"vejico med 0,10 in 10,0, <emphasis>odstotek</emphasis> med 1 in 1000 ali v "
"<emphasis>decibelih </emphasis> med -21 in +21."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7033
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use a factor above 1.0 (or percentage above 100 or more than 0 dB) if the "
"file is too silent, or a factor below 1.0 (percentage below 100 or less than "
"0 dB) if the file is too loud."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite faktor nad 1,0 (ali odstotek nad 100 ali več kot 0 dB), če je "
"datoteka pretiha, ali faktor pod 1,0 (odstotek pod 100 ali manj kot 0 dB), "
"če je datoteka preglasna."

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:7046
#, no-c-format
msgid "<replaceable>factor</replaceable>"
msgstr "<replaceable>faktor</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7048
#, no-c-format
msgid "A floating point value with the amplification factor."
msgstr "Vrednost s plavajočo vejico s faktorjem ojačanja."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7069
#, no-c-format
msgid "<entry>factor</entry>"
msgstr "<entry>faktor</entry>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7073
#, no-c-format
msgid "percentage"
msgstr "odstotek"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7077
#, no-c-format
msgid "decibel"
msgstr "decibel"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:7093
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_zero; (Zero Generator)"
msgstr "&no-i18n-plugin_zero; (Zero Generator - Ničelni generator)"

#. Tag: literal
#: index.docbook:7097
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-plugin_zero;"
msgstr "&no-i18n-plugin_zero;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This plugin has two modes of operation. If used without parameters it wipes "
"the current selection by overwriting it with silence. When used with two "
"parameters, it inserts some amount of silence at the start of the current "
"selection."
msgstr ""
"Ta vtičnik ima dva načina delovanja. Če se uporablja brez parametrov, "
"izbriše trenutni izbor tako, da ga prepiše s tišino. Ko se uporablja z dvema "
"parametroma, vstavi določeno količino tišine na začetku trenutnega izbora."

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:7119
#, no-c-format
msgid "length mode"
msgstr "način dolžine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Determines the units in which the <emphasis>length</emphasis> of the "
"inserted silence will be given."
msgstr ""
"Določa enote, v katerih bo navedena <emphasis>dolžina</emphasis> vstavljene "
"tišine."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Length of the silence to insert, in milliseconds, samples or percentage of "
"the length of the file, depending on the parameter <parameter>length mode</"
"parameter>."
msgstr ""
"Dolžina tišine za vstavljanje v milisekundah, vzorcih ali odstotkih dolžine "
"datoteke, odvisno od parametra <parameter>length mode</parameter>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:7177
#, no-c-format
msgid "Questions and Answers"
msgstr "Vprašanja in odgovori"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7185
#, no-c-format
msgid "What do I need to compile &kwave;?"
msgstr "Kaj potrebujem za prevajanje &kwave;?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Read in the <ulink url=\"&url_devel_requirements;\">developer documentation</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Preberite v <ulink url=\"&url_devel_requirements;\">dokumentaciji za "
"razvijalce</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7199
#, no-c-format
msgid "Which sound cards does &kwave; support?"
msgstr "Katere zvočne kartice podpira &kwave; podpira?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwave; does not need support for any special sound card. The sound card "
"only has to be supported by your operating system and &kwave; uses its "
"interface to the operating system's sound driver through an ALSA, "
"PulseAudio, Qt, or OSS interface."
msgstr ""
"&kwave; ne potrebuje podpore za nobeno posebno zvočno kartico. Zvočno "
"kartico morata podpirati samo vaš operacijski sistem in &kwave; uporablja "
"svoj vmesnik za gonilnik zvoka operacijskega sistema prek vmesnika ALSA, "
"PulseAudio, Qt, ali OSS."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Why does &kwave; consume more memory than it can be expected from the size "
"of the opened file?"
msgstr ""
"Zakaj &kwave; porabi več pomnilnika, kot je mogoče pričakovati glede na "
"velikost odprte datoteke?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The reason for this is that &kwave; internally stores all samples in 32-bit "
"integers. This was easy to program, made the application faster and a bit "
"more reliable. So if you load an 8-bit file with about one megabyte it will "
"consume about four megabytes. Maybe we will change this somewhere in the "
"future..."
msgstr ""
"Razlog za to je, da &kwave; interno shrani vse vzorce v 32-bitnih celih "
"številih. To je bilo preprosto za programiranje, zaradi česar je bila "
"aplikacija hitrejša in nekoliko bolj zanesljiva. Torej, če naložite 8-bitno "
"datoteko s približno enim megabajtom, bo porabila približno štiri megabajte. "
"Mogoče bomo to nekje v prihodnosti spremenili..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7235
#, no-c-format
msgid "Which sound formats does &kwave; support?"
msgstr "Kateri zvočne formate &kwave; podpira?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwave; currently supports .wav files with 8, 16 and 24 bits per sample, "
"with any number of channels (of course including mono and stereo). "
"Additionally it can import all file types that libaudiofile supports and "
"some other formats like Ogg/Vorbis and MP3."
msgstr ""
"&kwave; trenutno podpira datoteke .wav z 8, 16 in 24 biti na vzorec, s "
"poljubnim številom kanalov (seveda vključno z mono in stereo). Poleg tega "
"lahko uvozi vse vrste datotek, ki jih podpira libaudiofile, in nekatere "
"druge formate, kot sta Ogg/Vorbis in MP3."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7252
#, no-c-format
msgid "What if I have files with a format not supported by &kwave;?"
msgstr "Kaj pa, če imam datoteke v formatu, ki ga &kwave; ne podpira?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have to work on a different format, you can convert it into .wav "
"format. A good set of tools for this is in the <ulink url=\"&url_sox;\">SoX</"
"ulink> package, they have also some nice documentation!"
msgstr ""
"Če morate delati v drugem formatu, ga lahko pretvorite v format .wav. Dober "
"nabor orodij za to je v paketu <ulink url=\"&url_sox;\">SoX</ulink>, imajo "
"tudi nekaj lepe dokumentacije!"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7270
#, no-c-format
msgid "I get errors when I want to do playback?"
msgstr "Ko želim predvajati, se prikažejo napake?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Maybe you have chosen a combination of playback rate and sample size that is "
"not supported by your sound driver and / or sound hardware. Try playback "
"with 8 bits per sample and mono first, this should always work. Then try to "
"increase the bits per sample and stereo playback step by step. Note that "
"some playback rates are not at all supported by some sound hardware."
msgstr ""
"Morda ste izbrali kombinacijo hitrosti predvajanja in velikosti vzorca, ki "
"je ne podpira vaš zvočni gonilnik in/ali zvočna strojna oprema. Poskusite "
"predvajati z 8 bitov na vzorec in najprej mono, to bi moralo vedno delovati. "
"Nato poskusite povečati število bitov na vzorec in stereo predvajanje korak "
"za korakom. Upoštevajte, da nekatera zvočna strojna oprema sploh ne podpira "
"nekaterih hitrosti predvajanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7289
#, no-c-format
msgid "The playback seems to do something but I hear nothing?"
msgstr "Zdi se, da predvajanje nekaj naredi, vendar ne slišim ničesar?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Maybe you have forgotten to increase the volume of the playback channel. "
"&kwave; is not responsible for changing the playback volume."
msgstr ""
"Morda ste pozabili povečati glasnost kanala za predvajanje. &kwave; ni "
"odgovoren za spreminjanje glasnosti predvajanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7304
#, no-c-format
msgid "Some files are played with half-speed?"
msgstr "Nekatere datoteke se predvajajo s polovično hitrostjo?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7309
#, no-c-format
msgid "Try choosing a different sound playback device."
msgstr "Poskusite izbrati drugo napravo za predvajanje zvoka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7317
#, no-c-format
msgid "The playback sometimes is disturbed and interrupted?"
msgstr "Predvajanje je včasih moteno in prekinjeno?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7322
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You should increase the size of the playback buffer to get a \"smoother\" "
"playback (this also makes the playback control reacting a bit slower)."
msgstr ""
"Za \"bolj gladko\" predvajanje bi morali povečati velikost medpomnilnika za "
"predvajanje (zaradi tega se nadzor predvajanja tudi nekoliko počasneje "
"odzove)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7332
#, no-c-format
msgid "The playback does not stop if I immediately press the stop button?"
msgstr "Predvajanje se ne ustavi, če takoj pritisnem gumb za zaustavitev?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7338
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The reason for this is that the sound driver already has received some "
"playback data from &kwave; at the moment when you press the stop button. "
"Decrease the size of the playback buffer and it should react faster (but "
"makes interruptions more probable)."
msgstr ""
"Razlog za to je, da je zvočni gonilnik že prejel nekaj podatkov o "
"predvajanju iz &kwave; v trenutku, ko pritisnete gumb za zaustavitev. "
"Zmanjšajte velikost medpomnilnika za predvajanje in ta bi se moral odzvati "
"hitreje (vendar so prekinitve bolj verjetne)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7350
#, no-c-format
msgid "Is ALSA supported?"
msgstr "Ali je ALSA podprta?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7355
#, no-c-format
msgid "Yes, since v0.7.4 for playback and recording"
msgstr "Da, od v0.7.4 za predvajanje in snemanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"What about playback with 18, 20, 24 or 32 bits per sample or more than two "
"channels?"
msgstr ""
"Kaj pa predvajanje z 18, 20, 24 ali 32 bitov na vzorec ali več kot dvema "
"kanaloma?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7369
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is possible through the ALSA interface, since v0.7.4."
msgstr "To je mogoče prek vmesnika ALSA, od v0.7.4."

