#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7794
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Name of the album if the source is an album that consist of more medias."
msgstr "Ime albuma, če je vir album, ki je sestavljen iz več medijev."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7800
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Annotation"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Annotation"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7801 index.docbook:7871
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Provides general comments about the file or the subject of the file. If the "
"comment is several sentences long, end each sentence with a period. Do not "
"include newline characters!"
msgstr ""
"Zagotavlja splošne komentarje o datoteki ali predmetu datoteke. Če je "
"komentar dolg več stavkov, vsak stavek končajte s piko. Ne vključujte znakov "
"za novo vrstico!"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7808
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Archival location"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Archival location"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7809
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indicates where the subject of the file is archived."
msgstr "Označuje, kje je predmet datoteke arhiviran."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7814
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Author"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Author"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7815
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Identifies the name of the author of the original subject of the file. "
"Example: <quote>van Beethoven, Ludwig</quote>"
msgstr ""
"Identificira ime avtorja izvirne teme datoteke. Primer: <quote>van "
"Beethoven, Ludwig</quote>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7821
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Lower Bitrate"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Lower Bitrate"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7822
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specifies the lower limit in a VBR bitstream."
msgstr "Določa spodnjo mejo v bitnem toku VBR."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7827
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Bitrate Mode"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Bitrate Mode"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7828
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bitrate Mode (ABR, VBR, CBR, &etc;)"
msgstr "Način bitne hitrosti (ABR, VBR, CBR itd.)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7833
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Bitrate"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Bitrate"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7834
#, no-c-format
msgid "Nominal bitrate of the audio stream in bits per second"
msgstr "Nominalna bitna hitrost zvočnega toka v bitih na sekundo"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7839
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Upper Bitrate"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Upper Bitrate"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7840
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specifies the upper limit in a VBR bitstream."
msgstr "Določa zgornjo mejo v bitnem toku VBR."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7845
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Bits per Sample"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Bits per Sample"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7846
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specifies the number of bits per sample."
msgstr "Določa število bitov na vzorec."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7851
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;CD"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;CD"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7852
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of the CD, if the source is an album of more CDROMs"
msgstr "Številka CD-ja, če je vir album z več CD-ROM-i"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7857
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;CDS"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;CDS"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7858
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of CDs, if the source is an album of more CDROMs"
msgstr "Število CD-jev, če je vir album z več CD-ROM-i"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7863
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Commissioned"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Commissioned"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7864
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lists the name of the person or organization that commissioned the subject "
"of the file."
msgstr "Navede ime osebe ali organizacije, ki je naročila predmet datoteke."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7870
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Comments"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Comments"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7878
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Compression"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Compression"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7879
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sets a mode for compressing the audio data to reduce disk space."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi način za stiskanje zvočnih podatkov za zmanjšanje prostora na disku."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7885
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Contact"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Contact"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7886
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Contact information for the creators or distributors of the track. This "
"could be a URL, an email address, the physical address of the producing "
"label."
msgstr ""
"Kontaktni podatki za ustvarjalce ali distributerje skladbe. To je lahko URL, "
"e-poštni naslov, fizični naslov proizvajalca oznake."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7893
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Copyright"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Copyright"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7894
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Records the copyright information for the file. If there are multiple "
"copyrights, separate them by a semicolon followed by a space. Example: "
"<quote>Copyright Linux community 2002</quote>"
msgstr ""
"Zabeleži informacije o avtorskih pravicah za datoteko. Če obstaja več "
"avtorskih pravic, jih ločite s podpičjem, ki mu sledi presledek. Primer: "
"<quote>Copyright Linux community 2002</quote>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7901
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Copyrighted"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Copyrighted"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7902
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indicates whether the file is protected by copyright or not."
msgstr "Označuje, ali je datoteka zaščitena z avtorskimi pravicami ali ne."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7907
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Date"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Date"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7908
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the date the subject of the file was created. Example: "
"<quote>2001-12-24</quote>"
msgstr ""
"Podaja datum, ko je bila zadeva datoteke ustvarjena. Primer: "
"<quote>2001-12-24</quote>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7914
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Engineer"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Engineer"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7915
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows the name of the engineer who worked on the file. If there are multiple "
"engineers, separate the names by a semicolon and a blank."
msgstr ""
"Prikazuje ime inženirja, ki je delal na datoteki. Če je inženirjev več, "
"imena ločite s podpičjem in presledkom."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7922
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Estimated Length"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Estimated Length"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7923
#, no-c-format
msgid "Estimated length of the file in samples"
msgstr "Ocenjena dolžina datoteke v vzorcih"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7928
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Filename"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Filename"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7929
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name of the opened file"
msgstr "Ime odprte datoteke"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7934
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;File Size"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;File Size"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7935
#, no-c-format
msgid "Size of the file in bytes"
msgstr "Velikost datoteke v bajtih"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7940
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Genre"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Genre"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7941
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Describes the genre or style of the original work. Examples: <quote>classic</"
"quote>, <quote>pop</quote>"
msgstr ""
"Opisuje žanr ali slog izvirnega dela. Primeri: <quote>classic</quote>, "
"<quote>pop</quote>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7947
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;ISRC"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;ISRC"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7948
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"ISRC number for the track; see the ISRC intro page for more information on "
"ISRC numbers. &url_isrc;"
msgstr ""
"številka ISRC za skladbo; glejte uvodno stran ISRC za več informacij o "
"številkah ISRC. &url_isrc;"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7955
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Keywords"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Keywords"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7956
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Provides a list of keywords that refer to the file or subject of the file."
msgstr ""
"Ponuja seznam ključnih besed, ki se nanašajo na datoteko ali zadevo datoteke."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7962
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Labels"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Labels"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7963
#, no-c-format
msgid "The list of labels/markers."
msgstr "Seznam oznak."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7968
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Length"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Length"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7969
#, no-c-format
msgid "Length of the file in samples."
msgstr "Dolžina datoteke v vzorcih."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7974
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;License"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;License"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7975
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"License information, &eg;, <quote>All Rights Reserved</quote>, <quote>Any "
"Use Permitted</quote>, an URL to a license or the Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 "
"International (<quote>distributed under the terms of the Attribution-"
"ShareAlike 4.0 International License. See &url_cc_by_sa_4; for details</"
"quote>), &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Informacije o licenci, &eg; <quote>Vse pravice pridržane</quote>, "
"<quote>Dovoljena kakršna koli uporaba</quote>, URL do licence ali "
"Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International (<quote>distribuiran pod pogoji "
"Mednarodna licenca Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0. Za podrobnosti glejte "
"&url_cc_by_sa_4;</quote>), &etc;"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7985
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Medium"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Medium"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7986
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Describes the original subject of the file, where it was first recorded. "
"Example: <quote>orchestra</quote>"
msgstr ""
"Opisuje izvirno temo datoteke, kjer je bila prvič posneta. Primer: "
"<quote>orkester</quote>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7992
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Mime Type"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Mime Type"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7993
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mime type of the file format"
msgstr "Mime vrsta zapisa datoteke"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7998
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Emphasis"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Emphasis"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:7999
#, no-c-format
msgid "Audio emphasis mode"
msgstr "Način poudarka zvoka"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8004
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Layer"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Layer"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8005
#, no-c-format
msgid "MPEG Layer, I, II or III"
msgstr "MPEG sloj, I, II ali III"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8010
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Mode Extension"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Mode Extension"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8011
#, no-c-format
msgid "MPEG Mode Extension (only if Joint Stereo)"
msgstr "Razširitev načina MPEG (samo če je Joint Stereo)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8016 index.docbook:8144
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Version"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Version"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8017
#, no-c-format
msgid "MPEG Version, 1, 2 or 2.5"
msgstr "Različica MPEG, 1, 2 ali 2.5"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8022
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Name"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Name"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8023
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Stores the title of the subject of the file. Example: <quote>Symphony No.6, "
"Op.68 &quot;Pastoral&quot;</quote>"
msgstr ""
"Shrani naslov predmeta datoteke. Primer: <quote>Simfonija št. 6, op.68 &quot;"
"Pastoralna&quot;</quote>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8029
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Opus Frame Length"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Opus Frame Length"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8030
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opus Frame Length in ms (supported values are 2.5, 5, 10, 20, 40, or 60 ms)"
msgstr ""
"Dolžina okvirja Opus v ms (podprte vrednosti so 2,5, 5, 10, 20, 40 ali 60 ms)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8036
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Organization"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Organization"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8037
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Name of the organization producing the track (i.e. the <quote>record label</"
"quote>)"
msgstr "Ime organizacije, ki producira skladbo (tj. <quote>založba</quote>)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8043
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Original"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Original"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8044
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indicates whether the file is an original or a copy"
msgstr "Označuje, ali je datoteka izvirnik ali kopija"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8049
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Performer"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Performer"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8050
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The artist(s) who performed the work. In classical music this would be the "
"conductor, orchestra, soloists. In an audio book it would be the actor who "
"did the reading."
msgstr ""
"Umetnik(-i), ki je(-jo) delo izvajal(-i). V klasični glasbi bi to bili "
"dirigent, orkester, solisti. V zvočni knjigi bi bral igralec."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8057
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Private"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Private"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8058
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indicates whether the subject is private"
msgstr "Označuje, ali je zadeva zasebna"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8063
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Product"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Product"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8064
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the name or the title the file was originally intended for. "
"Example: <quote>Linux audio collection</quote>"
msgstr ""
"Podaja ime ali naslov, ki mu je bila datoteka prvotno namenjena. Primer: "
"<quote>zvočna zbirka Linux</quote>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8070
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Sample Format"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Sample Format"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8071
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Format used for storing the digitized audio samples. Example: <quote>32-bit "
"IEEE floating-point</quote>"
msgstr ""
"Format, uporabljen za shranjevanje digitaliziranih zvočnih vzorcev. Primer: "
"<quote>32-bitni IEEE s plavajočo vejico</quote>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8077
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Sample Rate"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Sample Rate"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8078
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of samples per second"
msgstr "Število vzorcev na sekundo"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8083
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Software"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Software"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8084
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Identifies the name of the software package used to create the file. "
"Example: <quote>Kwave v0.6.4-1</quote>"
msgstr ""
"Določa ime programskega paketa, uporabljenega za ustvarjanje datoteke. "
"Primer: <quote>Kwave v0.6.4-1</quote>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8090
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Source"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Source"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8091
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Identifies the name of the person or organization who supplied the original "
"subject of the file. Example: <quote>Chaotic Sound Research</quote>"
msgstr ""
"Določa ime osebe ali organizacije, ki je priskrbela izvirni predmet "
"datoteke. Primer: <quote>Raziskava kaotičnega zvoka</quote>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8098
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Source form"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Source form"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8099
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Identifies the original form of the material that was digitized. Examples: "
"<quote>Record/Vinyl/90RPM</quote>, <quote>Audio DAT</quote>, <quote>tape/"
"CrO2/60min</quote>"
msgstr ""
"Identificira izvirno obliko gradiva, ki je bilo digitalizirano. Primeri: "
"<quote>Record/Vinyl/90RPM</quote>, <quote>Audio DAT</quote>, <quote>case/"
"CrO2/60min</quote>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8106
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Subject"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Subject"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Describes the subject of the file. Example: <quote>Bird voices at early "
"morning</quote>"
msgstr ""
"Opisuje predmet datoteke. Primer: <quote>Ptičji glasovi zgodaj zjutraj</"
"quote>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8113
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Technician"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Technician"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Identifies the technician who digitized the subject file. Example: "
"<quote>Torvalds, Linus</quote>"
msgstr ""
"Identificira tehnika, ki je digitaliziral predmetno datoteko. Primer: "
"<quote>Torvalds, Linus</quote>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8120
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Track"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Track"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8121
#, no-c-format
msgid "Track of the CD if the source was a CDROM."
msgstr "Sled CD-ja, če je bil vir CD-ROM."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8126
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Tracks"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Tracks"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8127
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of tracks of the CD if the source was a CDROM."
msgstr "Število skladb na CD-ju, če je bil vir CD-ROM."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8132
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Channels"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Channels"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8133
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specifies the number of channels of the signal."
msgstr "Določa število kanalov signala."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8138
#, no-c-format
msgid "&no-i18n-tag;Base Quality"
msgstr "&no-i18n-tag;Base Quality"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Base quality of the compression in VBR mode"
msgstr "Osnovna kakovost kompresije v načinu VBR"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:8145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"May be used to differentiate multiple versions of the same track title in a "
"single collection. (&eg; remix info)"
msgstr ""
"Uporablja se lahko za razlikovanje več različic istega naslova skladbe v eni "
"zbirki. (&eg; informacije o remiksu)"

